tk.michaelmckey.microcontrollerremote.db

Class DataRepository

  • java.lang.Object
    • tk.michaelmckey.microcontrollerremote.db.DataRepository

  • public class DataRepository
extends java.lang.Object
    This is where all of the global data is stored.
    It manages retrieving and saving data(to both SQL and JSON)
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Michael McKey
